1
00:01:32,070 --> 00:01:34,930
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:37,970
[Episode 32]

3
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:42,350
Your Highness, watch out!

4
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:43,210
Your Highness!

5
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,420
What happened?

6
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,780
That mute girl is from Qiang State.

7
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:48,310
She poisoned Her Highness.

8
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,120
Summon the imperial physician!

9
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:49,479
No.

10
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,590
Bai.

11
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,210
Do you remember?

12
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,970
When two stars meet,

13
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:55,370
one is destined to fall.

14
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,960
If one of us

15
00:01:56,979 --> 00:01:58,200
must die

16
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:00,630
for the other to live,

17
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,760
that the survivor...

18
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,690
doesn't have to be me.

19
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,690
You want to trade

20
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,240
your life for his?

21
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:13,990
No, you can't.

22
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,280
I've made up my mind.

23
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,970
Stop trying to persuade me.

24
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,390
Leave us.

25
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:19,910
Your Highness.

26
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:21,840
-Your Highness.
-Allow us to have our final moments.

27
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,400
Leave!

28
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:24,030
Yes.

29
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:30,930
Let's go.

30
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,190
CEO Dan,

31
00:02:43,050 --> 00:02:44,110
I broke my promise.

32
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,900
I don't want to wait for the next life,

33
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,910
so you can't leave me either.

34
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,540
Your Highness.

35
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:43,540
Thank goodness.

36
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,890
You're finally awake.

37
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,120
How come I'm fine?

38
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:54,870
You...

39
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,930
What did you all do?

40
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,220
We didn't do anything.

41
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,810
Physician Xiao came

42
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,170
to check on your pulse.

43
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,960
The poison's effect only lasts a night.

44
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,850
So now,

45
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,410
you are basically fine.

46
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,050
So...

47
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,380
Flower never intended to kill me.

48
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,399
She only wanted to
threaten me with poison.

49
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,899
It seems so.

50
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:22,230
What about His Majesty?

51
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:23,720
What did Physician Xiao say?

52
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,580
His Majesty...

53
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,420
is still in a coma.

54
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,460
Your Highness!

55
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,590
Your Highness! Bad news!

56
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:34,670
The mute girl poisoned herself!

57
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:37,570
[Zhaoyang Palace]

58
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,970
We deserve to die.

59
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,530
She had poison hidden with her.

60
00:04:42,530 --> 00:04:44,120
We were negligent for a moment,

61
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,390
and she...

62
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,390
I don't blame you.

63
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,920
We should be blaming those
who gave her orders instead.

64
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,780
They wouldn't even spare a child.

65
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,250
I'll go see her.

66
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,760
Flower!

67
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,050
Flower.

68
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,310
Can you tell me

69
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:04,320
what poison did you take?

70
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,850
We'll find a way to save you.

71
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,090
Poison from Qiang State...

72
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,360
has no cure.

73
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:14,470
You silly child.

74
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,890
You knew there were
so many secret guards in the palace.

75
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:18,620
You knew you wouldn't succeed.

76
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,160
Why did you still do it?

77
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:23,810
If the Emperor were to die of illness,

78
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:27,380
you would become Great Xia's

79
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,630
highest noble.

80
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,550
To get revenge,

81
00:05:33,510 --> 00:05:35,320
I would have to kill you.

82
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,010
But I couldn't bear to do it.

83
00:05:43,450 --> 00:05:44,050
So...

84
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:47,630
you did this on purpose?

85
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,350
All of them said...

86
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,930
the people of Xia

87
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,200
are all bad.

88
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,680
They also said

89
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:04,090
as long as I become the queen's warrior,

90
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,410
I could reunite with my family

91
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,070
in heaven.

92
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:10,410
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

93
00:06:10,950 --> 00:06:11,640
But...

94
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:14,180
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

95
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,720
But...

96
00:06:14,970 --> 00:06:18,170
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

97
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:16,840
But what?

98
00:06:21,290 --> 00:06:23,980
♪ Then we transform ♪

99
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,780
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

100
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:32,790
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

101
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:31,150
But...

102
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,270
you remind me of my sister.

103
00:06:33,659 --> 00:06:36,000
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

104
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:39,430
♪ And let time freeze ♪

105
00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:39,800
Easy, Chu Wu.

106
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:40,850
She's just a child.

107
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:45,870
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

108
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,250
The soldiers are here.

109
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:43,159
You should run.

110
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:44,570
Don't steal anymore.

111
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,560
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

112
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:47,909
Don't be afraid.

113
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:51,090
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

114
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,490
I'll give you a name.

115
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,120
Let's call you...

116
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,310
Flower. How's that?

117
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,300
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

118
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:59,210
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

119
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,220
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

120
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:04,600
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

121
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,210
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

122
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:08,840
♪ We can dance together ♪

123
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:18,460
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

124
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,310
Sister.

125
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,420
My mom is here to pick me up.

126
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,030
I'm going home.

127
00:07:41,170 --> 00:07:43,700
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

128
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:47,040
♪ And let time freeze ♪

129
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:53,520
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

130
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,140
Flower?

131
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,070
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

132
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:58,570
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

133
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:57,750
Flower!

134
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,790
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

135
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,310
Flower!

136
00:08:00,810 --> 00:08:06,770
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

137
00:08:07,450 --> 00:08:08,620
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

138
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:12,250
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

139
00:08:12,730 --> 00:08:14,840
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

140
00:08:14,890 --> 00:08:16,410
♪ We can dance together ♪

141
00:08:16,470 --> 00:08:25,450
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

142
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:33,280
♪ Never looking back ♪

143
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:50,750
I have ordered men

144
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:53,200
to bury the child outside the city.

145
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:54,790
We will just tell the rest

146
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:56,510
that she has left the palace.

147
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,750
Your Highness,
please do not grieve too deeply.

148
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:03,480
You must take care of yourself.

149
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,370
Right now, everyone

150
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,650
is counting on you, Your Highness.

151
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,030
Bai.

152
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,590
You know what?

153
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,840
Since I came to this world,

154
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,120
people like Xu Yao

155
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,150
and Du Shan

156
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,720
were all killed.

157
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:27,090
Then Mei took her own life,

158
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:30,330
while Wang Zhao died for our country.

159
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,340
Later, Yong'er died tragically,

160
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:35,190
and Cen Jintian died of illness.

161
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,720
Mr. Bei had also passed away.

162
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:42,110
And now even Flower...

163
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,180
had died of poison.

164
00:09:47,330 --> 00:09:48,460
All the people I love

165
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,790
and cherish

166
00:09:55,290 --> 00:09:56,700
is leaving me.

167
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,400
If His Majesty too...

168
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,780
I wouldn't be able to hold on anymore.

169
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,650
Your Highness.

170
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,080
My Master said

171
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,210
he was sure I could help him.

172
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:21,470
He wouldn't be wrong.

173
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:27,060
I hope so.

174
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:48,480
Physician Xiao.

175
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,450
General Lin.

176
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,630
Has there been any new discovery regarding

177
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:54,480
the poison Her Highness had sent?

178
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,480
I applied the poison to a mouse's wound,

179
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,360
and the wound wouldn't heal
for a long time.

180
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,870
This effect is very similar to the poison

181
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,510
Tu'er used on his blade before.

182
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,910
It's just that the dosage is too low.

183
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:05,040
I was about to ask where you got it from.

184
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,870
The mute girl serving Her Highness

185
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:10,480
left this flower before she died.

186
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,140
I wonder...

187
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,860
if it has anything to do with this poison.

188
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:28,780
It does!

189
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:30,520
Great.

190
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,010
I'll get a painter

191
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:32,780
to copy it.

192
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:34,870
I'll dig to the ends of the earth

193
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:35,700
to find it.

194
00:11:35,990 --> 00:11:36,720
General Lin.

195
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:40,620
I think...

196
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,980
I've seen this flower before.

197
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:48,170
I heard you guys found a clue?

198
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,450
Physician Xiao said

199
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:54,000
he saw someone growing
this flower in the flower house.

200
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,550
This might be the key to curing
His Majesty's poison.

201
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,080
Found it!

202
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,130
Found it!

203
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:07,000
It was originally planted in the ground.

204
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,200
But perhaps the Imperial Medical Bureau
needed to plant other herbs,

205
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,530
so they moved it to a pot.

206
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:11,960
That's why we couldn't find it right away.

207
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,390
It matches these dried flowers.

208
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,520
No mistake about it.

209
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,300
But in this palace,

210
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:17,790
who else

211
00:12:18,310 --> 00:12:20,370
would grow flowers from Qiang State?

212
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:21,440
It's...

213
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,360
Consort Xie.

214
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:26,350
I've loved gardening since I was young.

215
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,240
I saw these in
the Empress Dowager's garden.

216
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,740
These are so rare,

217
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,030
so I thought I'd ask for a few sprigs.

218
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,350
These plants

219
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,900
were rare tributes from various countries.

220
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,170
Consort Xie,

221
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:38,880
you have good taste.

222
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:57,900
Your Highness.

223
00:12:58,510 --> 00:12:59,440
Physician Xiao,

224
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,150
you came just at the right time.

225
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,670
Could you take a look at this flower

226
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:04,600
and tell me the best way to plant it?

227
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:06,780
Be careful.

228
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,340
Thick roots,

229
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,890
slender leaves,

230
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,730
and bell-shaped flowers.

231
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:16,660
It grows well in damp, miasmic places,

232
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:19,000
and doesn't seem to be from our Great Xia.

233
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,030
You have a sharp eye, Physician Xiao.

234
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:23,840
These are flowers presented to the Empress Dowager
as tribute from foreign lands.

235
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,500
I remember Consort Xie saying

236
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,910
that she received this as a reward
from the Empress Dowager.

237
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:31,110
Now that you mention it, it rings a bell.

238
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:33,250
Before the Empress Dowager died,

239
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,920
she seemed to have made such a gesture.

240
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:41,340
It's exactly the same gesture
Flower made just now.

241
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:42,760
This is a gesture...

242
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:45,240
made by people of Qiang State to
pray for their souls to return home.

243
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:47,570
The Empress Dowager was from Qiang State?

244
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,700
No wonder.

245
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:52,430
She hated the late Emperor so much,

246
00:13:52,430 --> 00:13:53,830
yet she spared no cost

247
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,030
to manipulate the court

248
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,630
and bring chaos to Great Xia.

249
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:59,570
It turns out she was just like Flower,

250
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,370
both pawns of Qiang State.

251
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,100
Your Highness.

252
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:07,120
For the method of fighting poison
with poison, which we had discussed,

253
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,450
the missing ingredient

254
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:11,400
might be this plant right here.

255
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:19,850
Yong'er.

256
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:23,450
You really are the chosen one.

257
00:14:25,350 --> 00:14:26,560
This last hope...

258
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:30,560
has been with you all along.

259
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,770
Your Highness,

260
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:41,500
I have replicated it according to
the ancient formula.

261
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,760
You just have to sprinkle it on the wound.

262
00:14:46,090 --> 00:14:47,150
Are you confident?

263
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,750
Previously, when His Majesty

264
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,950
was stabbed by Tu'er,

265
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:52,320
not only did the wound heal,

266
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,730
but his headaches were also relieved.

267
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,790
This method of fighting poison with poison

268
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,390
should theoretically work,

269
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,120
but no one has actually tried it.

270
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:05,280
When in doubt between
advancing and retreating,

271
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:07,160
one should choose to advance.

272
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:08,050
He's awake.

273
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:13,320
Wanyin.

274
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:15,080
I'm here.

275
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,550
How are you?

276
00:16:23,310 --> 00:16:23,720
Fine.

277
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,360
Thank you.

278
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:25,670
And you?

279
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,670
It's been 197 days.

280
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,000
That's half a year.

281
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:47,200
I wonder how things are outside.

282
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,300
Your Highness.

283
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,720
You are...

284
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:07,109
It's me, Wu Jiadong, Your Highness.

285
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:12,130
How did you get in?

286
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:13,819
Your Highness,

287
00:17:15,589 --> 00:17:16,589
I am incompetent.

288
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,020
The guards here

289
00:17:18,060 --> 00:17:19,190
are incorruptible.

290
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,690
I waited for half a year,

291
00:17:22,069 --> 00:17:24,020
until chaos broke out outside

292
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,310
and people's resolve wavered.

293
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,960
Only then could I bribe my way through

294
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,960
to sneak inside

295
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,500
and see Your Highness.

296
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,080
Keep your voice down.

297
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:35,850
Don't you think...

298
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:40,880
there are eyes everywhere watching me?

299
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:44,210
-Your Highness. You...
-My every move...

300
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,640
is controlled by him.

301
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:51,590
Come on.

302
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:53,400
Here.

303
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,380
Look at this.

304
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,040
Sometimes...

305
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,770
the chess piece I place here

306
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,080
ends up somewhere else.

307
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,520
And...

308
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,760
the guards at the door,

309
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:10,000
they never change.

310
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:13,880
It's as if they have no friends,

311
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:15,880
no family,

312
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:18,560
and nothing else to do.

313
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,480
Their life's mission

314
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:24,510
seems to be just guarding me.

315
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:29,830
Sometimes,

316
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,410
in a haze of confusion,

317
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:38,390
I can still hear them
calling me Worthy Lord.

318
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:42,590
It's as if my life

319
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:45,140
has different versions.

320
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,270
One time,

321
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:51,830
they hailed 'Long live the Emperor.'

322
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:56,260
I managed Great Xia perfectly fine,

323
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,520
bringing peace and prosperity.

324
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:03,140
They all called me the true Son of Heaven.

325
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:09,870
There is an invisible hand in this world,

326
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:13,620
and we are all his pawns.

327
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:20,780
You certainly wouldn't understand,

328
00:19:22,170 --> 00:19:24,060
because you are a level below me.

329
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:24,730
Yes.

330
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:29,970
I'll show you right now.

331
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:33,920
It's time.

332
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:37,130
Someone will interrupt us any moment.

333
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:42,330
The guards are coming.

334
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:43,740
I must go.

335
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:49,590
Interesting.

336
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:55,900
Your Highness,

337
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:58,350
please take care.

338
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,870
You just have to wait a little longer,

339
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:03,600
and you will rise to power again.

340
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,680
I'll take my leave.

341
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,200
Interesting.

342
00:20:19,830 --> 00:20:22,480
You guys don't seem to be much good.

343
00:20:26,320 --> 00:20:27,950
I've got you!

344
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,240
I've got you!

345
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:39,070
Your Majesty,

346
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:41,090
Xiahou Bo actually believed it.

347
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:42,160
When I left,

348
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,480
he was still shouting that
he is the true...

349
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,610
the true... true...

350
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:47,860
What utter nonsense!

351
00:20:49,590 --> 00:20:51,020
From now on, go see him

352
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,370
every now and then.

353
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,060
Tell him

354
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,340
how chaotic the world outside is.

355
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:57,340
Make him wait.

356
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,130
As long as he lives,

357
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:02,590
I won't hold you accountable.

358
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,310
Thank you, Your Majesty,

359
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:06,580
for giving me a chance to redeem myself.

360
00:21:07,170 --> 00:21:08,090
You may leave.

361
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:09,910
Thank you, Your Majesty.

362
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:20,440
Speak your mind.

363
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,980
I don't understand.

364
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,260
Why are you doing this, Your Majesty?

365
00:21:28,050 --> 00:21:29,380
As long as there is hope,

366
00:21:29,510 --> 00:21:30,710
one won't seek death.

367
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:33,400
But Prince Duan committed treason first.

368
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,640
We are still brothers,

369
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,640
actual brothers.

370
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,520
Your Majesty,

371
00:21:39,870 --> 00:21:41,900
you are truly benevolent.

372
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:44,090
Don't force tears if you have none.

373
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,800
When did Wanyin leave the palace?

374
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,060
Why isn't she back yet?

375
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,900
Her Highness left only an hour ago.

376
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,200
That's too long. I'll go get her.

377
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:56,720
Yes.

378
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:00,650
Don't come with me.

379
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,220
Prepare hotpot for me.

380
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:04,440
We'll have the nine-grid pot tonight.

381
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,370
Yes.

382
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:09,160
-Stop!
-Slow down.

383
00:22:09,670 --> 00:22:10,400
Here, Er Lan.

384
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,900
Thank you, Your Highness.

385
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:18,610
Brother Cen.

386
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,280
Because of your Yan millet,

387
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:22,080
Great Xia survived the drought.

388
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:24,040
Now,

389
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:25,840
the war in Yan State has been quelled.

390
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:28,790
[Tomb of Wang Zhao]

391
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,790
Tu'er has become the Emperor of Yan,

392
00:22:27,790 --> 00:22:29,110
and had even sent a treaty of alliance.

393
00:22:28,850 --> 00:22:31,470
[Tomb of Du Shan]

394
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:31,720
An era of peace and prosperity
has arrived.

395
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:33,250
With you here, Brother Cen,

396
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:35,680
we will see abundant harvests every year.

397
00:22:36,590 --> 00:22:37,020
Slow down.

398
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:38,020
Let's take a walk.

399
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:39,680
Okay.

400
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:43,080
-Be careful not to fall.
-Let’s go over there.

401
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:46,240
Li Yunxi has been watching you
for quite a while now.

402
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,440
He even asked me about you a few days ago.

403
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,830
Are you trying to set us up,
Your Highness?

404
00:22:51,830 --> 00:22:53,090
I wouldn't go that far.

405
00:22:53,790 --> 00:22:55,560
What kind of life you want,

406
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,250
and who you want to be with,

407
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,600
is all up to you.

408
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:04,610
What's on your mind now?

409
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:06,490
Do you still want to leave?

410
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:09,720
Now that the imperial examinations
have resumed,

411
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:11,210
talented people are emerging in court.

412
00:23:11,210 --> 00:23:12,370
My departure now

413
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:14,200
can be seen as a graceful exit.

414
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,000
Look, look!

415
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,030
It's just...

416
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:21,900
I'm just a bit worried about you,
Your Highness.

417
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,590
After all, joint rule by
the emperor and empress

418
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,320
will inevitably cause gossip.

419
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:27,790
Your Highness' influence is at its peak,

420
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:29,590
so no one dares to challenge you.

421
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:32,680
But from now on, you'll be swamped with
daily affairs and countless tasks,

422
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,200
and even just a small mistake—

423
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,400
It doesn't matter if mistakes are made.

424
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,530
Achievements belong to Her Highness,

425
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:44,520
while any minor mistakes are mine.

426
00:23:44,550 --> 00:23:46,310
When loyal ministers offer counsel,

427
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:48,170
Her Highness will surely listen.

428
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,160
But...

429
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:52,480
If any treacherous schemers
seek to exploit the situation,

430
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,330
my madness

431
00:23:53,830 --> 00:23:55,390
can relapse at any time.

432
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,270
I might accidentally

433
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,400
kill someone in court again.

434
00:23:59,990 --> 00:24:01,940
You really know how to play along.

435
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:04,660
Greetings, Your Majesty.

436
00:24:04,660 --> 00:24:05,140
Rise.

437
00:24:06,270 --> 00:24:07,020
Alright.

438
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,480
Go back to the carriage and
stay out of the wind.

439
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,590
We're not done talking yet.

440
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,540
Let me listen in.

441
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:11,760
Go. Stop fussing.

442
00:24:14,310 --> 00:24:15,640
Okay, I'll go find them.

443
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:26,870
To be honest,

444
00:24:27,890 --> 00:24:29,690
I can't bear to let you go either.

445
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:34,230
[Tomb of Wang Zhao]

446
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,680
Now that Li Yunxi and Yang Duojie

447
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,190
are doing so well,

448
00:24:34,570 --> 00:24:36,300
are you willing to lose to them?

449
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,640
But now,

450
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:39,450
everyone knows I am a woman,

451
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:42,070
and there is no precedent
for female officials.

452
00:24:42,070 --> 00:24:43,240
There was never a precedent

453
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:45,310
for joint rule by both
the emperor and empress either.

454
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,240
For many things,

455
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:47,260
if we don't try,

456
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:49,450
how could there be any precedent?

457
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:50,040
Er Lan.

458
00:24:50,810 --> 00:24:52,610
Precisely because we are women,

459
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:54,950
we must remember.

460
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:56,280
For many things,

461
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:59,470
we should be the first to do them,

462
00:24:59,930 --> 00:25:01,280
not the last.

463
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:07,490
Li Yunxi was wrong about one thing.

464
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:09,720
He's not the only one in this world

465
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:10,920
who understands you.

466
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:16,910
With the great ambitions of yours
to make your mark in history,

467
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:18,970
why hide behind someone else's name?

468
00:25:20,030 --> 00:25:20,780
We women

469
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:23,680
can also achieve great things that

470
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,560
benefit the common people.

471
00:25:30,390 --> 00:25:31,250
Your Highness.

472
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,300
Go and play.

473
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:38,220
Also,

474
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:40,480
I am currently short-handed on my mission

475
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:43,030
to establish girls' schools
across the country.

476
00:25:43,030 --> 00:25:43,830
In the future,

477
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,160
little girls like her

478
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,260
can attend school just like boys.

479
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:48,050
Er Lan.

480
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,560
What do you think of this offer?

481
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,200
Aren't you tempted?

482
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:58,980
You are truly wise.

483
00:25:58,990 --> 00:25:59,920
You know right away

484
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:00,960
if it'll work or not.

485
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,750
Of course.

486
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:06,880
Did you catch a chill?

487
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,420
Why are your hands so cold?

488
00:26:15,730 --> 00:26:18,130
Don't frown on such a
beautiful spring day.

489
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,110
Didn't Physician Xiao mention that

490
00:26:21,110 --> 00:26:22,240
the poison in my body

491
00:26:22,370 --> 00:26:23,770
has been mostly cleared?

492
00:26:26,130 --> 00:26:27,160
Don't worry.

493
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:29,880
I will be with you for many, many years.

494
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:33,810
I told you to go back and wait.

495
00:26:33,810 --> 00:26:35,810
Couldn't you wait just for a moment?

496
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,650
I'll go back and drink ginger soup.

497
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,440
That's more like it.

498
00:26:43,590 --> 00:26:45,720
I don't want to live like that anymore—

499
00:26:46,030 --> 00:26:47,160
alone in the palace,

500
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:50,530
living in fear and dread, waiting for you.

501
00:26:58,350 --> 00:27:01,240
When one hears the woeful tune of
"Breaking the Willow Branch",

502
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:03,640
who wouldn't feel homesick?

503
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:06,200
Wherever you are

504
00:27:07,490 --> 00:27:09,190
is my home.

505
00:27:11,070 --> 00:27:12,590
Don't say such cheesy pickup lines

506
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:13,760
from now on.

507
00:27:17,780 --> 00:27:19,050
I meant in the future.

508
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:23,550
But today, I suppose I could make myself
listen some more.

509
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,680
Then I'll continue.

510
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:27,420
As for the future,

511
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,460
let's set a small goal first.

512
00:27:29,570 --> 00:27:30,900
Let's earn 100 million.

513
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:33,000
We'll then find an experienced driver

514
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:33,610
to take us

515
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:35,560
to travel around the world.

516
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:39,270
Your Majesty,

517
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,590
once we leave,

518
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:43,160
there's no one left
to play shuttlecock with you.

519
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,960
I will miss you all too.

520
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:48,240
But His Majesty insists on
disbanding the harem.

521
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,570
I tried to persuade him,

522
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,980
but his mind is made up.

523
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,560
There's nothing I can do.

524
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:55,200
We are not blessed with the good fortune

525
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:57,020
to serve His Majesty

526
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,650
and live and die with him.

527
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:02,720
You really want to live and die
with His Majesty?

528
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,720
Then how about...

529
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:05,890
I go plead with His Majesty again?

530
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:07,270
-No, no, no.
-No, no, no.

531
00:28:07,270 --> 00:28:09,800
That's really not necessary,
Your Highness.

532
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,960
After you leave the palace,

533
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,790
what do you all want to do?

534
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:15,110
Go home first, of course.

535
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:17,910
My parents were thrilled to hear
I was coming home.

536
00:28:18,070 --> 00:28:19,830
You still have a home to return to.

537
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:20,440
As for me,

538
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:23,700
I'll just have to find
another man to marry.

539
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:27,270
What's wrong with getting married?

540
00:28:27,270 --> 00:28:29,780
This time, I'll find someone I like.

541
00:28:30,110 --> 00:28:31,870
I want to have a real romance.

542
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:34,930
Sister, do you mean

543
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:36,780
you never liked His Majesty?

544
00:28:41,420 --> 00:28:43,020
The money His Majesty gave me

545
00:28:43,070 --> 00:28:45,340
is enough to open a shop in the capital.

546
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:47,830
I want to sell my rose essence.

547
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:50,440
My secret recipe will
surely make a fortune.

548
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:51,350
When the time comes,

549
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:53,280
all of you must come and support me.

550
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:54,510
Sure!

551
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:55,980
Alright.

552
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,840
No matter what you choose,

553
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:00,610
I hope that from now on,

554
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:02,320
you will live a smooth life.

555
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,130
All the best!

556
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,400
All the best!

557
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:34,350
♪ When the net of destiny
blocks the light ♪

558
00:29:34,730 --> 00:29:37,060
♪ Floating in the trap ♪

559
00:29:39,020 --> 00:29:40,710
♪ It's like a mystery ♪

560
00:29:42,260 --> 00:29:46,310
♪ But with the ending not yet determined ♪

561
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:49,340
♪ No one can define me ♪

562
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:53,020
♪ My whole life ♪

563
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:57,150
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

564
00:29:57,370 --> 00:30:00,200
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

565
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:01,310
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

566
00:30:01,330 --> 00:30:04,890
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

567
00:30:06,130 --> 00:30:07,640
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

568
00:30:07,670 --> 00:30:09,130
♪ I am the moral order ♪

